parameters.name: AssociateType
parameters.description:
The type of the resource with which the route table is associated. Valid values:

*   **VSwitch**
*   **Gateway**

parameters.name: EnsRegionId
parameters.description: The ID of the ENS node.

parameters.name: EnsRegionIds
parameters.description: The IDs of edge nodes. You can specify 1 to 100 IDs.

parameters.name: PageSize
parameters.description: The number of entries per page.

parameters.name: RouteTableId
parameters.description: The ID of the route table.

parameters.name: RouteTableName
parameters.description: The name of the route table.

parameters.name: Type
parameters.description:
The SNAT type.

*   FullCone: full cone NAT.
